   "source": [
    "# 在 Google Colab 上构建 Android APK\n",
    "\n",
    "## 使用步骤：\n",
    "1. 点击菜单 Runtime -> Run all\n",
    "2. 等待 15-20 分钟\n",
    "3. 下载生成的 APK 文件"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
